  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the beef strips and cook until browned, about 3-4 minutes.",
    "Remove the beef from the skillet and set aside.",
    "Add the chopped onion and bell pepper to the skillet and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the Croatian paprika and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Return the beef to the skillet and stir to combine with the vegetables.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
